column1: "I (Javier) want to start a new project called 'Community Mural: Phoenix History'. The due date is 2023-12-15, and it's high priority. I (Javier) want to depict the cultural history of Phoenix with other artists."
"On 2023-10-02, I (Javier) will sketch some initial ideas for the 'Community Mural: Phoenix History' project."
"On 2023-10-04, I (Javier) plan to visit the Phoenix Art Museum to gather inspiration for the mural."
"I (Javier) have an appointment on 2023-10-06 at 10:00 AM at the local community center with Maria Gonzalez to discuss the mural project."
"Every Monday, I (Javier) will spend two hours painting with my daughters San and Milly to keep my skills sharp."
"Met with Maria Gonzalez at the community center on 2023-10-06. We discussed the theme and logistics for the mural project."
"I need to buy art supplies for the mural project on 2023-10-08."
"On 2023-10-08, I (Javier) will research historical events in Phoenix to include in the mural."
"I (Javier) have a meeting with my daughters San and Milly on 2023-10-10 at 3:00 PM at our home to plan our contributions to the mural."
"Met with my daughters San and Milly on 2023-10-10. We decided to focus on the Mexican diaspora's influence on Phoenix for our part of the mural."
"On 2023-10-12, I (Javier) will visit the library to find books on Phoenix history."
"I (Javier) will start painting the background of the mural on 2023-10-12."
"I (Javier) have a call scheduled with the local artist community on 2023-10-14 at 11:00 AM to discuss collaboration."
"Spoke with the local artist community on 2023-10-14. They are excited to join the mural project."

"Every Monday, I (Javier) will continue painting with my daughters San and Milly."

"I (Javier) have a meeting with Maria Gonzalez on 2023-10-20 at 2:00 PM at the community center to review the sketch."
"On 2023-10-19, I (Javier) will prepare materials for the mural project."
"Reviewed the mural sketch with Maria Gonzalez on 2023-10-20. She suggested adding more details about the agricultural history of Phoenix."
"On 2023-10-22, I (Javier) will start painting the agricultural section of the mural."
"On 2023-10-22, I (Javier) will work on the mural's agricultural theme with my daughters San and Milly."
"I (Javier) have a call with the local artist community on 2023-10-24 at 10:00 AM to discuss progress."
"I (Javier) discussed the mural's progress with the local artist community on 2023-10-24. They are impressed with the work so far."
